==Bootleg culture==
Dream Theater have released a series of official bootlegs, demos, and other rarities through YtseJam Records, headed by Portnoy.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ytsejamrecords.com |title=YtseJam Records – The Official Dream Theater Bootlegs |publisher=Ytsejamrecords.com |date= |accessdate=January 2, 2009}}</ref>

===Demo series===
